      <ownedComment xmi:id="ffa33550-1084-4d97-a5ce-069f681c42ef" body="A use case model specifies the services a system provides to its users; that is, the different ways of using the system, and whose top-level package is a use case system." annotatedElement="9ac310a0-7b69-4191-b267-1561d3244faa">
